data.description: Fantastic Remodel Opportunity! Discover the tranquility of this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath split-level residence nestled on a sprawling 1/3 acre cul-de-sac lot with majestic mature trees. This property invites you to unlock its full potential and remodel to create your ideal home. As you step into the welcoming living room, natural light streams through a beautiful bay, picture window, offering picturesque views of the front yard. Imagine cozy evenings by the fireplace in the basement family room, featuring a distinctive beamed ceiling and a brick fireplace with a raised hearth – a perfect spot for relaxation and gatherings. With a partially finished basement, this home provides an excellent opportunity for your personal touch and creative vision. The layout allows for versatile use, providing room for a home office, workout area, or additional entertainment space. Embrace the joy of outdoor living with a large deck that beckons for barbeques and entertaining. The expansive backyard provides plenty of space for outdoor games, gardening, or simply enjoying the weather and nature. Located in a desirable cul-de-sac, this property ensures a peaceful and private living experience while still being conveniently close to all that Canton has to offer. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into your dream home – a place where memories are made and cherished. Seize the opportunity to do a fantastic remodel and make this property uniquely yours!
